      "rationale": "At MRL 5 with Class III device, ASME V&V 40 requires Gradation 4 SQA. The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024R1) is validated under ISO 9001:2015 QMS with full version-controlled release notes, regression test suite (>2400 tests, 100% pass rate), and FDA-recognized software validation documentation. User-defined hemolysis scalar transport UDFs are under configuration management with unit tests and code review records. SQA level 4 achieved.",
