      "rationale": "Code verification performed via Method of Manufactured Solutions (MMS) for the Navier-Stokes solver and the hemolysis scalar transport equation. Observed order of convergence (p=1.97 for momentum, p=1.89 for scalar) consistent with theoretical second-order accuracy. Benchmark problems (lid-driven cavity Re=1000, pipe flow with analytical solution) reproduced to within 0.3%. Gradation 4 achieved.",
