      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented in FDA pump testing protocol with full traceability. Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water, viscosity matched to 37°C whole blood) characterised with rheometer measurements at each test temperature. Pump geometry confirmed by CMM measurement of test article with tolerance report. All five operating points verified against pump performance curve with uncertainty <2% on flow rate and <1% on speed. Gradation 4 achieved.",
