      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison performed using both feature-based metrics (NIH mean absolute error 0.0031 g/100L, 12% maximum relative error) and statistical validation metrics (u-pooled validation comparison per ASME V&V 20). Validation uncertainty U_val computed and compared to required validation accuracy. At all five operating points, |E| < U_val, confirming the model is validated within the required accuracy for the COU. Gradation 5 achieved, exceeding the required Gradation 4.",
