      "rationale": "Iterative convergence monitored via residual norms and QoI monitors. All residuals converged to <1×10⁻⁶ (continuity, momentum, scalar). NIH monitor showed <0.1% change over final 500 iterations. Round-off error assessed by double-precision comparison; negligible contribution (<0.01% of NIH). Floating point consistency verified across parallel decompositions (4, 8, 16 cores) with NIH variation <0.05%. Gradation 4 achieved, exceeding required Gradation 3.",
