      }
    },
    {
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "All model inputs characterised with probability distributions for Monte Carlo UQ. Blood viscosity from rheometer measurements (n=12, 95% CI ±8%). Power-law coefficients from published experimental data with documented uncertainty bounds. Geometry from FDA pump CAD file with CMM-verified tolerances. Inlet velocity profiles from LDV measurements at pump inlet. Input uncertainty propagated through 10,000-sample Monte Carlo; all inputs documented in the UQ report with traceability to measurement records. Gradation 4 achieved.",
