      "rationale": "Experimental hemolysis measurements performed with porcine blood from six independent donors, processed within 24 hours of collection. Hematocrit standardised to 35±2% for all tests. Six replicate runs per operating point on the same test article; test article inspected by CMM before and after testing with no detectable wear. Blood analog (glycerol-water) used for PIV validation with viscosity matched to ±3% of whole blood at 37°C. Sample provenance and storage documented. Gradation 3 achieved.",
